Description: Next Biometrics Group ASA is a Norway-based company active in the field of technology. The Company provides high-security fingerprint sensor technology for authentication. Next Biometrics Group develops products for four different market segments: Public Security, Access control, Office and Notebooks, Payments and Fintech. The Companyâ€™s offering includes such products as Next Biometrics FAP20 Sensor, Next Biometrics Access 100 Pro Reader and Development Kit for STM32. Next Biometrics Group offers also dual authentication methods to customers looking for both face and fingerprint biometric solutions. The Company has several wholly owned subsidiaries, including NEXT Biometrics AS, NEXT Biometrics China Ltd, NEXT Biometrics Taiwan Ltd, and Biometrics Solutions India Pvt Ltd.
